&control
    calculation = 'relax'
    prefix = 'mos2monorel'
    outdir = './mos2monorel/'
    pseudo_dir = './pseudos/'
    etot_conv_thr = 1.0d-5
    forc_conv_thr = 1.0d-4
    verbosity   = 'high',
    tprnfor = .true.
    tstress = .true.
/

&system
    ibrav=0,
    nat=3, 
    ntyp=2, 
    ecutwfc=40,
    ecutrho = 400,
    occupations = 'smearing',
    smearing = 'mv',
    degauss = 0.02,

/

&electrons
    conv_thr=1.0d-8
    mixing_beta = 0.3,
    electron_maxstep = 200,
/

&ions
    ion_dynamics = 'bfgs'
/

&cell
    cell_dofree='all'
/

ATOMIC_SPECIES
  Mo  95.95  Mo.UPF
  S   32.06  S.UPF

CELL_PARAMETERS (angstrom)
3.1840   0.0000   0.0000
-1.5920  2.7574   0.0000
0.0000   0.0000  18.15

ATOMIC_POSITIONS (crystal)
Mo  0.3333  0.6666  0.0868553232
S   0.666666667 0.333333333 0.0007840135
S   0.666666667 0.333333333 0.1729231052

K_POINTS (automatic)
  6 6 1 1 1 1